--doorman_protocol      Specify which doorman instance to connect to. This doorman instance
 *   --doorman_host          is used for both reading and sending data.
 *   --doorman_port
 *
 *   --lighthouse_site              Specify data to select. By default, dollface stops sending data
 *   --lighthouse_sensor            when there is not more activity.
 *   --lighthouse_timestamp
 *   --lighthouse_end_timstamp
 *
 *   --dollface_site            How dollface advertises itself
 *   --dollface_sensor


